  Worktree 018f-act
  active - isolated - agent agent-ac waitingOnUser - /tmp/project/.codewith/worktrees/018f-actions-worktree

› 1. Read details                  Show lease, path, branch, cleanup, and owner state
  2. Use in current session        Retarget the current session cwd to this managed worktree
  3. Start agent here              Prefill a background-agent start command for this worktree
  4. Open owning agent             Open the background-agent action menu for this worktree owner
  5. Merge candidate               Dry-run merge this worktree into the current target
  6. Release                       Release this worktree and retain it on disk
  7. Cleanup                       Release and delete if the worktree is clean
  8. Back to worktrees             Return to all managed worktrees

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
